categories: Category:Enlisted stormtroopers of Darth Krayt's Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A stormtrooper of Joker Squad was on Ossus in 137 ABY, exploring the ruins of the world's Jedi Academy. At least four other Jokers were there. Along with Private Orland, the stormtrooper searched the jungle outside of the temple. After the Jokers found nothing and reported a fruitless search to their superiors, Darth Stryfe ordered an orbital bombardment anyway.

Five stormtroopers in total are shown exploring the ruins in the seventeenth issue of Star Wars: Legacy. One issue previously, three are shown, with one of them going unnamed. It is possible that said unnamed trooper is the character described in this article.
